WEBVTT

00:06.760 --> 00:10.760
'Hello.
Tindall? Moriarty.

00:10.760 --> 00:14.720
'I've been calling you for
hours. I was engaged.'

00:16.680 --> 00:19.320
'What happened? Did she leave you?

00:21.000 --> 00:24.240
'I'd rather not discuss
it over the telephone.'

00:26.560 --> 00:30.000
'I'm glad I caught you. I'm planning
to steal the Mona Lisa.

00:30.000 --> 00:32.960
'I'll need an accomplice,
and you were in the frame.'

00:34.520 --> 00:37.880
'The Mona Lisa? Isn't she guarded?

00:39.160 --> 00:41.960
'Well, if that smile
is anything to go by...

00:43.720 --> 00:47.360
'Where shall we meet?
In Paris, of course!

00:47.360 --> 00:49.560
'I shall loiter outside the Louvre.'

00:53.240 --> 00:54.920
Anybody there?

00:56.000 --> 01:02.074
